## Constraints

- Count public items mechanically — don't guess.
- Estimate behavior conservatively — err on the side of undercounting.
- Flag all red flags even if the depth score is acceptable.
- Do not execute arbitrary Python code in Jinja2 expressions (sandboxed execution).
- Handle missing variables gracefully (leave as-is or use default if specified).

